{"tid":1640363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無手足覺得左膠其實係對家扮？","createTime":"2019-10-09T02:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T02:53:29.000Z","uid":83933,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"28503d7876239e3e61c6d6d76c186260dc7ea34e","tid":1640363,"uid":83933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:35:58.000Z","msg":"永遠手足比人打比人捉左膠永遠唔見人，之後有啲咩事就保護對家同報警拖後腿拉自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正常一個左膠邊敢行咁前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗屌我分化撚，我從來無當過左膠係自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d018d1f3d7d8e95ed6531014dd23355f35c0f9c","tid":1640363,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG1sQ5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG1sQ5b.jpg&h=d6b3d577&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9NvORS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9NvORS.jpg&h=fcaaa2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球「和尼畫」#XinniethePooh Challenge<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Xinnie the Pooh」Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on instagram, facebook and twitter with tag #Xinnie the Pooh<br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to ask them draw together!<br />\n5. Those who are tagged also join to draw Xinnie the Pooh, keep drawing until Chairman Xi can see our works!!"},{"pid":"bfcd2304ff068ed8c93b24b1880c4d1ebfdd3843","tid":1640363,"uid":83933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:43:16.000Z","msg":"之前比人誤會係鬼嘅前線手足都上黎解過畫，但啲左膠次次係度幫對家，從來無解釋點解要咁做，但下次私了果時又會自動出現"},{"pid":"eb077be2e2e079820c7ae0032b5a63d15b358182","tid":1640363,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 證明左膠係欺善怕惡"},{"pid":"192d6322c3aca951c7d9e130a7b29dd613db1af3","tid":1640363,"uid":83933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb077be2e2e079820c7ae0032b5a63d15b358182","tid":1640363,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 證明左膠係欺善怕惡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:47:42.000Z","msg":"個的士狗果50萬真係有40萬要歸功佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99ab35749ea2f5fdc33f0b3dfb31a7a8d6d65ce","tid":1640363,"uid":146520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:49:40.000Z","msg":"有，前日沙田打支那國旗狗直情有條灰衫便衣叉手足條頸<br />\n之後上咗狗車"},{"pid":"6288ee0fe2019840746f732ffd6afb4d4a4a0098","tid":1640363,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:50:39.000Z","msg":"左膠同陣地都係ON9"},{"pid":"8a6f549fdac5ad84333f2b0341d474806d0004c5","tid":1640363,"uid":34990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:51:35.000Z","msg":"事實上係有，早兩日沙田個個灰衫左膠跟埋上狗車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大波man出黎撩人打次次都跟住個肥婆社工扮左膠"},{"pid":"99e3db48c99d2fe25c73b3d85667693be95c8b25","tid":1640363,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:53:29.000Z","msg":"其實唔同位置都有<br />\n前線 後勤 文宣 冷氣軍師 左膠 屌左膠"}]}